{"tid":1159803,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋光引玊] 攝影大師談香港美學","createTime":"2019-05-18T03:50:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T05:32:06.000Z","uid":35780,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9a2e192600c2c4e747ab186d7d1eb29e13cc819e","tid":1159803,"uid":35780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T03:50:57.000Z","msg":"今日睇到一條短片，入面講啲野幾好，覺得幾值得分享。<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://mbasic.facebook.com/video_redirect/?src=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft42.9040-2%2F60848974_337627570259745_418500419321331712_n.mp4%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26efg%3DeyJybHIiOjMyOSwicmxhIjo3ODUsInZlbmNvZGVfdGFnIjoic3ZlX3NkIn0%253D%26_nc_ht%3Dvideo.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3D69e76a1b333e760cfd93c970277a025e%26oe%3D5CDFB524&amp;source=misc&amp;id=2394241450634367&amp;refid=52&amp;__tn__=FH-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmbasic.facebook.com%2Fvideo_redirect%2F%3Fsrc%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fvideo.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%252Fv%252Ft42.9040-2%252F60848974_337627570259745_418500419321331712_n.mp4%253F_nc_cat%253D104%2526efg%253DeyJybHIiOjMyOSwicmxhIjo3ODUsInZlbmNvZGVfdGFnIjoic3ZlX3NkIn0%25253D%2526_nc_ht%253Dvideo.fhkg3-1.fna%2526oh%253D69e76a1b333e760cfd93c970277a025e%2526oe%253D5CDFB524%26source%3Dmisc%26id%3D2394241450634367%26refid%3D52%26__tn__%3DFH-R&d=LRk9npnliL4HefRMP%2BWOkHfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=9a3a0aeb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mbasic.facebook.com/video_redirect/?src=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft42.9040-2%2F60848974_337627570259745_418500419321331712_n.mp4%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26efg%3DeyJybHIiOjMyOSwicmxhIjo3ODUsInZlbmNvZGVfdGFnIjoic3ZlX3NkIn0%253D%26_nc_ht%3Dvideo.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3D69e76a1b333e760cfd93c970277a025e%26oe%3D5CDFB524&amp;source=misc&amp;id=2394241450634367&amp;refid=52&amp;__tn__=FH-R</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n【PHOTOGRAPHY】《美紙》專訪：盧玉瑩的香港美學<br />\n作為六、七十年代的攝影先驅，盧玉瑩小姐曾經為《號外》、《大特寫》等雜誌拍攝菲林照片，後來協助創辦《電影雙週刊》，經她手拍過的小人物大明星都不計其數。除了攝影師和傳媒人的身分，她還曾經擔任中學美術設計的老師，教曉身邊人「識得睇靚嘢」。<br />\n<br />\n對於香港美學的變遷，她絕對有資格說話。"},{"pid":"1a3cc7db4cb66b96989f3f4ed09221fd1017d0cd","tid":1159803,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:02:23.000Z","msg":"有時真係俾個地方大細所限<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人又迫<br />\n香港人本身生活空間細，接觸嘅嘢自然少啲<br />\n當然有錢去外國旅行係會見識多咗，但係一般人總唔會個個月去旅行，同埋旅行又點同生活<br />\n外國地方你離市中心少少已經好多活動空間"},{"pid":"7cb6498566965d0014cbbb7324fe96b6b6f142ce","tid":1159803,"uid":50502,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:07:45.000Z","msg":"香港人審美：是但影街影樓+個文青filter= 靚相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b66df3807505a196f23924ebeb8547ef69309f7","tid":1159803,"uid":88886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:20:58.000Z","msg":"大缸圈<br />\n好矇<br />\n<br />\n怪叫"},{"pid":"1218ea8da48115862961b8ba5d12e80defad8735","tid":1159803,"uid":12176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1a3cc7db4cb66b96989f3f4ed09221fd1017d0cd","tid":1159803,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:02:23.000Z","msg":"有時真係俾個地方大細所限<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人又迫<br />\n香港人本身生活空間細，接觸嘅嘢自然少啲<br />\n當然有錢去外國旅行係會見識多咗，但係一般人總唔會個個月去旅行，同埋旅行又點同生活<br />\n外國地方你離市中心少少已經好多活動空間"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:25:30.000Z","msg":"噏乜？好似離晒題"},{"pid":"229edbe284281bd020dd5fb414102c9c9bb082a0","tid":1159803,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T08:40:44.000Z","msg":"條link手機入唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e8d23d564fbed0c7c005ffdd65cf28b594b541","tid":1159803,"uid":14625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a3cc7db4cb66b96989f3f4ed09221fd1017d0cd","tid":1159803,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T04:02:23.000Z","msg":"有時真係俾個地方大細所限<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人又迫<br />\n香港人本身生活空間細，接觸嘅嘢自然少啲<b